comments:
i noticed that all of the words ended with - yckoh- making easier to learn the shapes by only remembering the letters at the start. For remembering the shapes I only let my head come up with random associations, like the circle being with only round letters and the start with pointy letters.
The hard part was the section were I had to communicate with another user, mostly because while recalling the shapes was easy at that point, there was no way to indicate a particular color, making it a bit of a guessing game.
